
# Star Topology

## Description
The star topology is a network design where all devices are connected to a central hub or switch. Communication between devices passes through this central point.

## Characteristics
- Easy to configure and expand by adding new devices.
- If one cable fails, only the connected device is affected.
- Weakness: if the central hub fails, the entire network goes down.

